Privacy
# Privacy Policy
Last Updated: December 12, 2023
## 1. FACE DATA PROCESSING AND PRIVACY
### 1.1 Face Data Collection and Use
- We collect ONLY temporary facial feature points for real-time face swapping
- All processing is done locally on your device
- Face data is used ONLY for providing the face swap feature
- No biometric data is collected or stored
- No facial recognition database is created or maintained
### 1.2 Face Data Storage and Retention
- Face data exists only during active processing
- Immediately deleted after face swap completion
- No cloud storage or transmission
- No permanent storage of any face-related data
- No backups of face data are created
### 1.3 Face Data Security
- All processing occurs locally on your device
- No face data is transmitted over networks
- No face data is shared with third parties
- Industry-standard encryption for all operations
- Secure memory management during processing
### 1.4 User Control Over Face Data
- Face detection is optional and requires explicit permission
- Users can disable face detection at any time
- Users maintain full control over their photos
- Clear opt-out options available
## 2. GENERAL INFORMATION COLLECTION
### 2.1 User-Provided Information
- Photos uploaded for face swapping (temporary, local processing only)
- App preferences and settings
- Premium subscription details (if purchased)
- Device permissions granted
### 2.2 Automatically Collected Information
- Device information (model, OS version)
- App usage statistics
- Crash reports
- Performance metrics
## 3. HOW WE USE INFORMATION
We use collected information to:
- Provide face swapping functionality
- Improve app performance and features
- Process payments for premium features
- Provide customer support
- Send important updates and notifications
- Maintain app security
## 4. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
We work with:
- RevenueCat: Payment processing
- Google AdMob: Advertisement delivery
- Firebase: Analytics and crash reporting
- Apple: App Store services
Important Note: None of these services receive any face data or processed images.
## 5. DATA SECURITY
We implement:
- Industry-standard encryption
- Secure local processing
- Regular security updates
- Best practices for data protection
- Strict access controls
## 6. USER RIGHTS
You can:
- Control app permissions
- Opt-out of analytics
- Request data deletion
- Manage face processing features
- Cancel premium subscriptions
## 7. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY
- App is not intended for users under 13
- We don't knowingly collect children's data
- Special protections for all facial processing
- Immediate deletion of any inadvertently collected data
## 8. DATA STORAGE
### 8.1 Photos and Face Data
- Temporary processing only
- Local device processing
- Immediate deletion after processing
- No cloud storage
- No data retention
### 8.2 Other Data
- User preferences: Stored locally
- Payment info: Handled by Apple/RevenueCat
- Analytics: Non-personal aggregated data
## 9. CHANGES TO POLICY
- Users will be notified of significant changes
- Updates posted in app and website
- Email notification for major changes
- 30-day notice for material changes
## 10. CONTACT INFORMATION
For privacy questions or concerns:
- Email: info@furkancingoz.com
